991
01:14:50,663 --> 01:14:52,573
<font color="yellow"><i>Apa dia memberikan jawabannya padaku?</i></font>

992
01:14:53,533 --> 01:14:55,603
<font color="yellow"><i>Atau dia sedang bertanya?</i></font>

993
01:14:59,024 --> 01:15:00,354
<font color="yellow"><i>Lupakan aku.</i></font>

994
01:15:23,494 --> 01:15:25,524
<font color="yellow"><i>Kau pasti sangat kesepian.</i></font>

995
01:15:27,754 --> 01:15:29,524
<font color="yellow"><i>Maafkan aku.</i></font>

996
01:15:34,254 --> 01:15:36,494
<font color="yellow"><i>Kutanya, apa dia itu memang Yeo.</i></font>

997
01:15:37,294 --> 01:15:38,954
<font color="yellow"><i>Dia akhirnya datang.</i></font>

998
01:15:43,594 --> 01:15:46,094
<font color="yellow"><i>Aku akan melakukannya sekarang.</i></font>

